ion of insults due to sexual orientation or gender identity.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The statement\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 844}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"the artists\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the Debilly catwalk\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"unprecedented wave\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"hatred\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"the trivialisation\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"insults\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual orientation\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"gender identity\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Stop Homophobia lawyers have received numerous reports of incitement to hatred, insults, online harassment, threats and defamation.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Homophobia lawyers\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous reports\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"incitement\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"insults\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"online harassment\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"defamation\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The firm was contacted by Mr Karl Sanchez, known as Nicky Doll, with a complaint in defamation filed against Mr. Laurence Fox and other users of the social network X (Twitter).\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurence Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r